限为 7 年期, 债券利息按年支付。 2023 年内蒙古自治区政府再融资一般债券 (十一期 ) 发行金额为 194.4 亿元，品种为记账式固定利率附息债券, 债券期限为 5 年期，债券利息按年支付。 文件显示，按照财政部要求，债券资金纳入一般公共预算管理，募集资金全部偿还政府负有偿还责任的拖欠企业账款。 文件表示，将政府隐性债务问责作为专项整治的重要内容，组织开展财经秩序专项整治行动，进一步发挥隐性债务问责闭环管理机制作用，对化债措施不实、新增隐性债务进行严肃问责，发挥典型案例警示教育作用。打响化债第一枪！内蒙古：拟发行 663.2 亿元特殊再融资债券，全部用于偿还拖欠企业账款"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-3cda4c702ea8cc322bb98618acb529a6_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "220 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/624007903"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIwpWpufLv6tInEAMaCTEwMDk0NzUzNyCWqs+oBjAAOP0BQANyCTYyNDAwNzkwM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1695824860.770467", "card_id": "EV_12220991", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "北京年薪 35 万互联网和老家 10 万的公务员，该如何选择？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-e97fb56beff0d1111b02ada43bba8383_720w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "207 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/theater/12320"}, "tag_area": {"normal_url": "", "night_url": "", "width": 0, "height": 0}}, "attached_info": "ClgIwpWpufLv6tInEBgaBDc2Nzkg9MDQqAZABHIIMTIyMjA5OTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZMoBI2h0dHBzOi8vd3d3LnpoaWh1LmNvbS90aGVhdGVyLzEyMzIw"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1695824860.770483", "card_id": "Q_288783218", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1356}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "新疆到底有多干燥？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": 